dist/
release/
node_modules/
.DS_Store
*.log
# Bundled CLI SEA staging - release workflows write the signed/staged
# binary into a per-arch directory such as
# `resources/cli/darwin-arm64/`. These directories contain a large
# signed binary plus a `version.json` and must not be committed. We
# match arch directories specifically so the explanatory placeholders
# in `resources/cli/` itself (`.gitkeep`, `README.md`) stay tracked.
resources/cli/*/
